- ( groaning )

191
00:19:08,500 --> 00:19:09,416
( chuckles )

192
00:19:13,916 --> 00:19:15,166
( groans )

193
00:19:29,041 --> 00:19:30,000
- ( breathes shakily )

194
00:19:42,833 --> 00:19:46,250
- ( breathes shakily )

195
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:13,000
- Mireille's voice:
"THE MAN WITHIN THE MAN.

196
00:20:13,083 --> 00:20:14,958
THE LOVE
WITHIN THE LOVE.

197
00:20:15,041 --> 00:20:17,375
THE SIN WITHIN THE SIN.

198
00:20:17,458 --> 00:20:20,208
THE HERMIT TOLD
UNTO THE SINNER,

199
00:20:20,291 --> 00:20:22,750
THE SOLDATS IS
WITH THE TRUTH."

200
00:20:24,458 --> 00:20:25,708
THE SOLDATS.

201
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:29,708
SO THAT'S THE NAME...

202
00:20:29,791 --> 00:20:30,958
OF OUR ENEMY.

203
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:38,416
- HUH?

204
00:20:45,625 --> 00:20:49,000
- BACK HOME...
IN CORSICA,

205
00:20:49,083 --> 00:20:51,583
MY PARENTS AND OLDER BROTHER
WERE ALL MURDERED.

206
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:57,416
TO THIS DAY I HAVE NO IDEA
WHO KILLED THEM OR WHY.

207
00:20:59,125 --> 00:21:02,208
THAT WAS THE LAST TIME
I SAW THIS WATCH...

208
00:21:03,541 --> 00:21:06,583
UNTIL YOU BROUGHT IT TO ME
FROM MY PAST.

209
00:21:08,166 --> 00:21:10,083
- BUT NOW I HAVE NOTHING.

210
00:21:13,666 --> 00:21:15,083
I'M SORRY.

211
00:21:17,333 --> 00:21:19,083
I'M SORRY, MIREILLE.

212
00:21:23,208 --> 00:21:24,125
- ( chuckles )

213
00:21:40,666 --> 00:21:42,791
I WILL OPEN
THIS DOOR TO THE PAST.

214
00:21:43,958 --> 00:21:46,625
I SWEAR I WILL.

215
00:24:00,333 --> 00:24:02,083
- ( woman singing
in Japanese )

